earning aptitude\">Language-learning aptitude</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Critical_period_hypothesis\" title=\"Critical period hypothesis\">Critical period hypothesis</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Motivation_in_second-language_learning\" title=\"Motivation in second-language learning\">Motivation</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Willingness_to_communicate\" title=\"Willingness to communicate\">Willingness to communicate</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Foreign_language_anxiety\" title=\"Foreign language anxiety\">Foreign language anxiety</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Metalinguistic_awareness\" title=\"Metalinguistic awareness\">Metalinguistic awareness</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">Strategies</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Language_learning_strategies\" title=\"Language learning strategies\">Language learning strategies</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Communication_strategies_in_second_language_acquisition\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Communication strategies in second language acquisition\">Communication strategies</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Code-switching\" title=\"Code-switching\">Code-switching</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Good_language_learner_studies\" title=\"Good language learner studies\">Good language learner studies</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\"><a href=\"/wiki/Theories_of_second-language_acquisition\" title=\"Theories of second-language acquisition\">SLA hypotheses</a></th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-even hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Competition_model\" title=\"Competition model\">Competition model</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/